Better Than Bouillon *Organic* in both chicken and beef is soy, gluten, and dairy free at the time of this review.<br /><br />As someone with severe food allergies, it took me ages to find a soup base that didn't have one of  them. Its nice that the one I finally found is truly excellent. I use these products often and always have excellent results.<br /><br />I find the chicken base a little on the sweet side, but nothing I can't work around.
